          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-19768 obd: add job_stats/exports netlink",
        "message": "LU-19768 obd: add job_stats/exports netlink\n\nAdd netlink handlers for per-client export statistics and\nper-job counters. The export handler iterates connected clients\nand emits NID, nodemap name, and lprocfs counter datasets. The\njob_stats handler walks the job_stat RB-tree under RCU and\nstreams each job's counters.\n\nA function-pointer indirection (nodemap_test_nid_fn) is used to\nresolve NID-to-nodemap without creating a circular dependency\nbetween obdclass.ko and ptlrpc.ko.\n\nChange-Id: I03f455a028fc65d364659f698799ef32cecd1a57\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@thelustrecollective.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
